metadata.name: VENDETTA #1
metadata.description:
Nude and raw feminine beauty portrayed on 35mm analog film.

“You have safely closed your window, dark room, I cross the universe when I paint, how to look at you and smile inside, insights can be superficial. Cross galaxies in seconds, forming knots, my dreams fall slowly”.

(3000x2000px JPG) Motion picture.

Muse: Evelyn Vendetta.
